---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Professional Artistry">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 py-16 md:py-24 prose prose-invert prose-ivory font-body">
    <h1 class="font-headline italic text-5xl ivory-text uppercase tracking-tighter">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="italic text-flt-muted opacity-50 uppercase font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest mb-12">Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
    
    <p>At Fun Lovin Tattoo, we value your privacy. This policy outlines how we handle your data when you visit our studio or use our professional mobile services.</p>
    
    <h2 class="font-headline italic text-3xl ivory-text uppercase">Data Collection</h2>
    <p>We collect only the necessary information to process your bookings and ensure safety standards (e.g., name, contact details, and relevant health disclosures for tattooing).</p>
    
    <h2 class="font-headline italic text-3xl ivory-text uppercase">Usage</h2>
    <p>Your data is used strictly for appointment scheduling and regulatory compliance. We do not sell or share your information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
    
    <h2 class="font-headline italic text-3xl ivory-text uppercase">The Portfolio</h2>
    <p>We may photograph completed works for our professional portfolio and social media, only with your explicit consent.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
